d:
Blazing sun, crashing waves, a white bikini.
On a holiday shore, Fubuki encounters a “familiar stranger.” A single mistake pries open a fracture between her pride and her desire. For the future of her organization, she is forced to choose between reason and humiliation. When silence turns into a transaction and power becomes a bargaining chip, Fubuki takes a step from which there is no return.

This chapter centers on psychological tension, imbalance of power, and forbidden temptation. Through a steadily tightening NTR atmosphere, it lays bare her hesitation, her struggle, and her descent in full.

Patreon exclusive. Miss it, and it’s gone.
